revision.text:
==Career== In 2016, Jumayyil was seen in Ali Shifau-directed romantic comedy ''[[Vaashey Mashaa Ekee]]'' opposite Majudha. In the film, she played the role of Ziyad, a person with a very different taste of his partner.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.avas.mv/12504 |title=A new Film, A new Lover, A new Jumayyil |language=Dhivehi |publisher=''Avas'' |author=Nadheem, Ahmed |date=8 January 2016 |archiveurl=http://web.archive.org/web/20160609164655/https://www.avas.mv/12504 |archivedate=9 June 2016 |accessdate=9 June 2016}}</ref> His performance was positively mentioned in the reviews, Ahmed Nadheem from ''Avas'' picked Jumayyil as the only actor who has shown a major improvement in acting compared to his previous works. He further rated Jumayyil at the same level of Majudha—whom Nadheem considered as the best actor of the film.<ref name="unlimited praise">{{cite news|url=https://avas.mv/15516 |title=Vaashey Mashaa Ekee: Unlimited praise |language=Dhivehi |publisher=''Avas'' |author=Nasheem, Ahmed |date=6 April 2016 |archiveurl=http://web.archive.org/web/20160606080851/https://avas.mv/15516|archivedate=6 June 2016 |accessdate=6 June 2016}}</ref>
