==Accolades== {| class="wikitable plainrowheaders sortable" |- !scope="col"| Year !scope="col"| Award !scope="col"| Category !scope="col"| Nominated work !scope="col"| Result ! scope="col" class="unsortable"| {{Abbr|Ref(s)|Reference(s)}} |- |rowspan="3"| 2017 ! scope="row" rowspan="3" | [[8th Gaumee Film Awards]] |rowspan="2"| [[Gaumee Film Award for Best Actor|Best Actor]] | ''[[Vaashey Mashaa Ekee]]'' | {{won}} |style="text-align:center;"|<ref name=GFA8win>{{cite news|url=https://mihaaru.com/entertainment/28345 |title="Vaashey Mashaa Ekee" wins majority awards |language=Dhivehi |work=Mihaaru |last=Adhushan |first=Ahmed |date=20 December 2017 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180330182244/https://mihaaru.com/entertainment/28345 |deadurl=no |archivedate=30 March 2018 |accessdate=30 March 2018}}</ref> |- | ''[[Emme Fahu Vindha Jehendhen]]'' | {{nom}} |style="text-align:center;"|<ref name=GFA8nom>{{cite news|url=https://mihaaru.com/entertainment/28015 |title=8th Gaumee Film Awards: Dark Rain leads nomination |language=Dhivehi |work=Mihaaru |last=Adhushan |first=Ahmed |date=12 December 2017 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180330160950/https://mihaaru.com/entertainment/28015 |deadurl=no |archivedate=30 March 2018 |accessdate=30 March 2018}}</ref> |- | [[Gaumee Film Award for Best Male Debut|Best Male Debut]] | ''Aniya'' | {{won}} |style="text-align:center;"|<ref name=GFA8win/> |- |}
